  "text": "Previous work has shown that bulk cloud models tend to underestimate sulfate formed via the O 3 pathway by underestimating pH and thus underestimating the fraction of S(IV) that is in the form of !\" ! !! . [CITATION_1] developed a parameterization to correct for the underestimate in cloud pH by comparing a bulk cloud model with a cloud model that resolves the heterogeneity in cloud chemistry. The uncertainty in this parameterization, and thus the degree to which it might result in an overestimate of the contribution of O 3 to in-cloud sulfate formation in GEOS-Chem is difficult to assess.",
