      "span_text": "Previous work has shown that bulk cloud models tend to underestimate sulfate formed via the O 3 pathway by underestimating pH and thus underestimating the fraction of S(IV) that is in the form of !\" ! !! . [CITATION_1] developed a parameterization to correct for the underestimate in cloud pH by comparing a bulk cloud model with a cloud model that resolves the heterogeneity in cloud chemistry.",
